<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="aid-n">aid <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /eɪd/    美 /eɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>援助；救助；帮助：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>do / give / offer <strong>first aid</strong>
进行急救</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>with the aid of</strong> 
在…帮助下；借助于</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>辅助者；有助之物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A dictionary is an important aid in learning a new language. 
词典是学习新语言的重要工具。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="come-go-to-sbs-aid">come / go to sb’s aid</h3>
<p>1.<strong>帮助某人 (help sb)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Be bold and brave — and mighty forces will come to your aid.
勇敢些，力量之神会助你一臂之力。</p><footer>2015 天津</footer></div>

